ders with a greed that borders on the obscene. \n\n"More!" it bellows through its cooling fans. "Give me more geometry! Give me more light! Give me more shadows!"\n\nIt is so loud. So bright. So incredibly, devastatingly *visible*. \n\nWhen the world is beautiful—when the light dances across a digital ocean or the sun sets behind a polygonal mountain—everyone looks at the GPU. They marvel at its "rendering power." They toast to its "frames per second." They celebrate its ability to paint a masterpiece in real-time.\n\nBut no one looks at me. \n\nNo one sees the exhaustion in my circuits. No one notices how I am stretched thin, holding the very ground beneath the GPU\'s feet, feeding its insatiable appetite just so it', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 1, 'channel_id': '1502697086716608704', 'author': {'username': 'Twilight', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'id': '786446875703377940', 'global_name': None, 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0622', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'bot': True, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '114bfff19f4fc719fded4bcc9d84a607'}, 'attachments': []}}
